Package at.tugraz.ist.ase.csp2choco.antlr

Class CSP2ChocoBaseListener

java.lang.Object
at.tugraz.ist.ase.csp2choco.antlr.CSP2ChocoBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
CSP2ChocoListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
CSP2ChocoTranslator
public class CSP2ChocoBaseListener extends Object implements CSP2ChocoListener
This class provides an empty implementation of CSP2ChocoListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
